snippet.title: Let's Sing 2024 - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Let's Sing 2024 is available now on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X/S. Watch the launch trailer to see what to expect with this karaoke game, featuring a new career mode and more.
